high_descs: Turn around and go near the dining table.
Take the egg plant from the dining table.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the egg plant into the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Placed the egg plant into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the dining table on your right.
Pick up watch from the egg plant.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the fridge.
Place egg plant on the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Cooling down egg plant by keeping on the fridge

high_descs: Head towards the egg plant on the dining table to your left
Pick up the egg plant from the dining table
Turn left and hang a right and cross the room, then head towards the fridge on your right
Put the egg plant on the lower shelf of the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put an egg plant in the fridge
